{"tid":1944673,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"傳 iPhone狗 恢復生產   業內人士指 Apple 與中國比亞迪集團簽約","createTime":"2020-03-26T14:10:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T23:51:53.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9c603c7013c11f11b30fff5f76b48046c152dc2e","tid":1944673,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:10:45.000Z","msg":"據外媒消息，因武漢肺炎疫情影響其生產進度的 iPhone 9（ iPhone SE 2）已恢復生產，預計最快會在 4 月底發表。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n受武漢肺炎影響，生產工作不斷延遲，一些核心零組件的供應不穩，導致原計劃在 3 月發佈的 iPhone 9 一直未能順利量產。不言，近日有業內人士指出，Apple 已經與中國比亞迪集團簽定新合約，以擴大生產規模和加快生產速度，但暫時未知比亞迪將會為蘋果代工哪些產品。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n而分析師 Jon Prosser 亦在其 Twitter 上爆料，指 iPhone 9 已經開始量產，更指信息可靠性為 100%。他在上週曾預測 Apple 快將推出新產品，而 Apple 的確在本週發布了新款 iPad Pro 和 MacBook Air。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n此次，Apple 即將發表的低價新 iPhone 包含兩款機型，分別是 iPhone 9 和 iPhone 9 Plus。iPhone 9 的售價預計在 3,000 人民幣（約港幣 HKD$3310 元）左右，而 iPhone 9 Plus 起步價約 3,300 人民幣（約港幣 HKD$3640 元）左右。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/03/26/iphone9-2/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F03%2F26%2Fiphone9-2%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWRyPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=24329aa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/03/26/iphone9-2/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"69da58e0e1beabcf9fe3b07d3138acb53b02603a","tid":1944673,"uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:12:21.000Z","msg":"2月講3月<br />\n3月講4月"},{"pid":"b347834acb84d7cec6bfbe4e0dfd6bc9b813f3c2","tid":1944673,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:24:44.000Z","msg":"黃定藍？唔識答"},{"pid":"bbfe9ed4368277570f4b264f1b672fff43ef63f3","tid":1944673,"uid":160891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:26:44.000Z","msg":"搬去北韓你咪又係照買，得把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9604329efaa1abfbad70c67849c977b111831fec","tid":1944673,"uid":44107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:38:40.000Z","msg":"四月week3 $3999"},{"pid":"ae35d5409716c370f2b4e4c4e54e3afb711d0f91","tid":1944673,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:39:41.000Z","msg":"比亞迪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />爆炸電池"},{"pid":"86322c8b3f021e8dd7c7103b1e22fe9af4c1e668","tid":1944673,"uid":9398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:48:54.000Z","msg":"屌你老母傳撚夠未啊冚家剷，<br />\n成撚日要做呢d手法去引人留意apple未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc08fdb290f9e3dcd6cc03d7c2029cda8763ef3","tid":1944673,"uid":104793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9604329efaa1abfbad70c67849c977b111831fec","tid":1944673,"uid":44107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:38:40.000Z","msg":"四月week3 $3999"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T23:51:53.000Z","msg":"我估4月15或之後<br />\n8同8 plus 既升級版"}]}